property.Description En:
Located just in one step from the Bang Tao beach this three bedroom private pool apartment is a member of the unique Laguna estate - Angsana Beachfront Residences. 
You open the living room sliding doors to let some fresh air in and thats when it strikes you  the ocean breeze, the sound of crashing waves, the rays of setting sun. Nature pools you, invites you to take a step outside and you accept. You walk past the swimming pool, unlock the gate and the moment you take a step past it, your feet sink into the white sand of the beach, your eyes rest on the horizon, your mind enters a blue, oceanic state. 
This is not just a dream, its vision of whats to come for the lucky owners of apartments at Angsana Beachfront Residences  Banyan Tree Groups first branded condominium in Thailand.
One unit in particular caught our attention, a three-bedroom pool residence located on the gourd floor. With 3 bedroom, 3 bathrooms and a total area of 341 sqm its a real beauty, and then it comes with a direct access to the beach bringing the vision presented above closer to reality. 
This and all the other properties making up the exclusive Angsana project have been designed in a uniquely Thai style, that blends traditional architecture with its lush, tropical surrounding and takes full advantage of its beachfront setting on Bang Tao Beach.
The project consists of two and three-bedroom units, with only two units per floor. Each residence offers expansive indoor and outdoor living spaces as well as a private swimming pool at the fringe of its broad terrace. Secure parking for residents and their guests is also provided.
But its not just what it is, its also where it is. Owning property set within Laguna Phuket complex comes with benefits  those who invest in Angsana Beachfront Residences receive membership of the Sanctuary Club - a global network of more than 40 resorts and hotels, 60 spas and 80 retail galleries, as well as a Laguna Phuket Golf Club membership.
Angsana Phuket Resort will provide the owners with management support, along with an array of services and amenities, including villa hosts. Additionally, Angsanas team of experts will help the owners reap maximum benefits through long and short-term rentals. 
Thats a lot of value for a single project. But when you dream, why not dream big?

property.Description En:
The villa has a distinct aesthetic quality that fits within the islands landscape perfectly - its tropical, its lush, it blends contemporary design with traditional elements, and above all  its welcoming. 
This effect is largely due to the materials used throughout the project  natural wood, best exemplified by the slender columns supporting the terrace roof; natural stone tiles use in the outdoor spaces, all this helps build an organic connection between spaces and those inhabiting it. A cool colour pallet further boosts this connection by creating a calming, at-ease ambience. 
Botanica Villas come in three to five bedrooms variants with usable areas from 440 to 650 sqm with generous land plots. These, however, are just numbers  what matters is the sensation of unrestrained, open space that they boast.
The developer realized, that the purpose of a Phuket home is not to cut oneself off from the surrounding nature but to be able to experience it deeper, to enjoy it and the way the villas are designed to reflect this premonition. The spacious indoors, with their high ceilings and panoramic windows, harmoniously connect with the lush-green outdoor areas; the infinity edge pool glimmers like a forest pond and all this natural beauty can be enjoyed in any weather, from the covered terrace. This is the place where nature and architecture become one.

complex.Description En:
Laguna Park is an inspired development of townhomes and villas in Phukets most desired residential neighborhood. Set adjacent to the world famous Laguna Phuket, this location combines stylish modern living with the  tranquillity of a relaxed island lifestyle. Homeowners can also enjoy privileged access to a residents beach club area and discounts within Laguna Phuket at the nearby Banyan Tree Phuket, Angsana Laguna Phuket, Cassia Phuket and Laguna Phuket Golf Club.
The three-storeyed Laguna Park Townhomes have been specifically designed with smaller families and couples in mind. These modern 2 and 3 bedroom properties offer a modern and functional living space, But homeowners can also completely reconfigure the top floor to create more room at their convenience. Add study, create extra bedroom or install a Jacuzzi.
The three-storeyed detached Laguna Park Villas are the largest homes in the estate. As well as four bedrooms including a spacious master bedroom, each Villa features multiple living spaces along with maids quarters that include a separate entrance. The same as with Townhomes, the top floor can be completely transformed to add a fifth bedroom, extra dining room or more living space. For those wanting to soak up Phuket's glorious tropical sunshine, the top floor can be used to install a rooftop pool or barbecue area. 
All Laguna Park owners will receive a number of privileged benefits. These include access to the residens' exclusive beach club area and generous discounts on amenities within Laguna Phuket, including hotels, restaurants, bars, golfing and spa facilities. Villa owners will also receive a 5 year golf membership to the Laguna Golf Phuket or 5 year vacation club membership to Angsana vacation club.
With superb leisure facilities, beachside restaurants and relaxing retreats sitting on your doorstep, Laguna Park homeowners can enjoy a lifestyle that most can only dream about. 

In general Laguna Phuket - Asia's first integrated destination resort - is a holiday paradise of deluxe hotels and villas spanning 1,000 acres of tropical parkland.
Facilities and activities include spas, restaurants, bars, boutique shopping, private charter and join-in luxury tours, daily activities at most Laguna Phuket hotels, canoeing, sailing, resort golf, and (of course) the pristine beaches and azure waters of the Andaman Sea. Whether you're travelling with friends, vacationing with family or planning a romantic escape, Laguna Phuket offers something for everyone with ample opportunities for fun, romance, relaxation and exploring.
Laguna Phuket provides its dwellers with a perfect balance of quietude and household comfort, as well as with free shuttle bus service (every 20 minutes), which takes you to Bang Tao beach, canal shops, restaurants, gym, beach clubs, hotel private beaches and other facilities.
Phuket island offers a wonderful environment to work and live  combining warm tropical weather and an easy-going lifestyle with the modern amenities of 21st century life. Laguna Phuket itself is located in a prime west coast area of Phuket with proximity to an abundance of facilities. Local shopping malls, international schools and world-class hospitals are all close by, while Phukets international airport can be reached by car in just 20 minutes.

ABOUT DEVELOPER 
Laguna Resorts & Hotels Public Company Limited acquired Laguna Phuket site in the early 1980s, turning what was a barren tin mine into Laguna Phuket, Asias first integrated resort complex.
The company listed of the Stock Exchange of Thailand in 1993 and has gained a reputation as a responsible developer whose interest combine hotels and real estate.
Today, Laguna Property, the property development arm of the company has formed itself as the largest and most established developer on Phuket with a respective international presence, and gained a strong industry reputation, combining interests in hotels and real estate with the emphasis on quality and environmental protection. Its continued success has been consistently recognized through the years with numerous environmental and tourism awards.

complex.Description En:
Almost two decades ago a vision was born. A vision of a home that is close to nature and close to the owners hearts. Today its clear that reality outgrew the vision. And it keeps growing.
In 1999, Phuket had already been one of the worlds most popular tourist destinations for roughly two decades, but its transition into a developers paradise was yet to take place. To conceptualize a large property project then, required courage and vision. Turns out that thats exactly what developers of the largest premium property estate in Nai Harn area were blessed with.
It began as just 12 villas on a land plot of 22 Rai (35 200 sqm). But it also started as an idea  an idea to allow the home owners to take an active part in the design process of their own homes, with the assistance from the developers architect. The proof that it worked is in the pudding  by now more than 100 villas have been built and the total area has reached almost 200 Rai (320 000 sqm) turning the project into one of the largest up-market development in Nai Harn. 
What made it work? First and foremost  strong foundations. The project has been and still is developed responsibly, with an emphasis on international standards of construction quality, delivered by the developers own builders team. Properly built and carefully maintained, it still looks as good as new. But thats not all. Located close to Nai Harn beach and a short distance from Rawai, it not only provides the residents with easy access to multiple shops, restaurants, and many other commercial and community facilities but also manages to retain precious privacy and remain close to nature, taking advantage of its spacious green surroundings to provide tranquil environment with surrounding hillside and mountain views. Here convenience meets nature.
Four elements played a leading role in the developers vision. First are the Design and Space. The propertys design takes full advantage of the surrounding environment, its natural ventilation and maximizes living space in the name of comfort. Function comes next, with the project offering all conveniences of modern living. This is followed by Quality, which results from the developers experience and skills, to support both construction and maintenance. And last but not least is the Environment, with nearly half of the land area reserved for the natural landscape. No wonder that the project has been constantly gaining value, which increased by as much as 400% since its launch.
One important factor positively affecting that upwards trend is the way the property is managed by the professional team. A wide range of property management services on offer include 24-hour security, common area maintenance, villa assistant services, letting services and other aspects of residential services and maintenance  all this done with the view of long term value gain for both individual property and the entire development.

This wonderful condominium is set on the hills between Surin and Bang Tao beaches offering amazing panoramic sea view over two best bays on the north-west of Phuket. The award winning design team created a special living space blending authentic Thai art with modern living. The development comprises wide range of facilities, including four roof top sea view and two ground floor swimming pools, beautifully landscaped gardens, clubhouse and library, waterfalls and fountains, exceptional dining and first class SPA center. The project is located in the southern part of Phuket Island in 500 metres to Rawai beach and 2,5 kilometres to Nai Harn beach. Rawai area is popular with many tourists from Italy, France, Russia, Korea, China and Thailand. In last two years, the holiday rental requirement of this area has increased twice at least. complex.Description En:
Located within 2 minutes of the main entrance to the Laguna 5 star resort and residential  complex, on the west coast of Phuket, the estate offers world class restaurants on the doorstep, with easy access to golf club and miles of sandy beach, yet only in a 20 minutes drive from Phuket International Airport. A new water and recreation park is being developed in a 5 minutes of the estate, delivering entertainment options for the owners and their guests.
The estate comprises a total of 25 single storey pool villas, set in lush tropical gardens. Each villa offers a private sanctuary of comfort and style. Park right at the front door and  access your villa, via discrete private entrance. The pool and garden beckon, while the elegant layout and design confirm you are here to relax. Pitched roofs over the major living areas emphasize the tropical lifestyle.
Step down from the dining area to a sunken living room, opening onto the terrace by the pool. Full length windows and sliding doors bring the tropical greenery and cooling breezes to your seat.
The layout of the villa ensures privacy in all bedrooms, with the master bedroom looking down the length of the pool, while other bedrooms look over the garden. Each bedroom has its own ensuite bathroom, with a Jacuzzi bath in the master suite.
Property in Phuket, especially in the immediate vicinity of Laguna area and Bang Tao beach is highly sought after for holiday rentals. Developer offers a rental management program for the owners, interested in receiving a regular rental yield. 
Since 2003, this proven Phuket developer, has delivered high quality villas, starting with his experience as a major shareholder and director of 75 villas estate and another 24 villas estate, all in Bang Tao area.

complex.Description En:
This estate holds the most desirable address in Phuket and will recognize 26 elite pool residences with bespoke villa designs and usable areas of 440  650 square meters to accommodate up to four bedrooms.The pristinely manicured Bang Tao and Laguna neighborhood hosts numerous family oriented activities and is dotted with a plentitude of boutique shops and restaurants along this 8 km stretch of white sand.
Developer offers a custom built residence that will take approximately twelve months to construct. It offers flexible payment plans to support overseas buyers. Payment schedule is linked to the completed stages of home construction.
Each villa centers around a natural stone tiled swimming pool with a free-flowing floorplan that is capped by a vaulted, teak wood ceiling and framed by concertina glass doors. The transom windows above these glass doors give added light and elegance to the main area of the home. To celebrate the idyllic outdoor ambience the eave has been overextended to create an added lounge or dining area on the terrace which is supported by striking pillars. The grand tile flooring in the front room matches that on the terrace for a seamless transition to the outdoors.
The developer has been developing private homes on Phuket for over twelve years and have applied architectural genius into creating a sanctuary living environment filled with calmness and beautiful nature  scenery. For the investor, the developer can guarantee five years of rental income. A reception office and Caf at the main entrance to this estate will be operated by an established Tour Operator which will manage all aspects of the holiday rentals for an effortless return on the investment.
